-HAVE YOU THOUGHT THIS THROUGH?

35:40.790 --> 35:42.052
-YEAH, WHAT DO YOU MEAN?

35:42.183 --> 35:43.750
-IF IT GOT OUT
THAT THOSE TWO COPS

35:43.880 --> 35:45.708
