35:48.668 --> 35:49.712
-YOU THINK?

35:49.843 --> 35:51.018
-PUT YOURSELF IN THEIR SHOES.

35:51.149 --> 35:51.975
HOW WOULD YOU FEEL?

35:52.106 --> 35:53.499
YOU CAN'T EMBARRASS THEM

35:53.629 --> 35:55.196
BY MAKING THIS RESCUE
PUBLIC KNOWLEDGE.

35:55.327 --> 35:58.678
