CAN DOUBLE-TEAM HIM.

36:38.892 --> 36:40.415
-OKAY.

36:45.072 --> 36:47.379
-ED?
-WHAT?

36:47.944 --> 36:50.425
-ED?
-HEY, BIG GUY!

36:50.556 --> 36:52.688
YOU'RE JUST IN TIME FOR
MY NEXT EXTRAVAGANZA.

36:52.819 --> 36:54.299
-WE NEED TO TALK TO YOU.

36:54.429 --> 36:56.257
-HEY, YOU KNOW WHAT A
STUNT MAN'S MOTTO IS?

36:56.388 --> 36:57.389
-NO.

36:58.259 --> 37:01.306
-WHY GO THROUGH A DOOR WHEN
YOU CAN GO THROUGH A WINDOW?

37:02.132 --> 37:03.351
THATS WHAT STUNT
MEN ALWAYS SAY,

37:03.482 --> 37:05.440
AND, WELL I AM A STUNT MAN.

37:06.093 --> 37:07.747
HEY, WHAT DO YOU THINK
OF THE OLD SET HERE, TOO?

37:07.877 --> 37:10.140
IT'S THE OLD WESTERN SALOON
THING, I BUILT IT MYSELF.

37:10.271 --> 37:11.620
-YEAH, YEAH, IT'S REALLY NICE.

37:11.751 --> 37:12.186
BUT LOOK, JESSIE
WANTS HER MONEY BACK.

37:12.317 --> 37:13.709
-YEAH.

37:13.840 --> 37:14.971
-UH, WELL, I'M AFRAID
I CAN'T DO THAT.

37:15.755 --> 37:17.931
I GOT IT ALL INVESTED IN
THE SET AND MY WARDROBE.

37:18.061 --> 37:19.541
BUT I AM GONNA DEMONSTRATE

37:19.672 --> 37:21.108
HOW TO GO THROUGH
A GLASS WINDOW,

37:21.239 --> 37:22.544
JUST LIKE THEY
DO IN THE MOVIES.

37:22.675 --> 37:24.111
COURSE THERE IS A
LITTLE SECRET TO IT,

37:24.242 --> 37:25.547
I BET YOU DON'T KNOW
THAT, LITTLE DARLIN'.

37:25.678 --> 37:26.418
-YEAH, THE GLASS IS
MADE OUT OF CANDY?

37:27.419 --> 37:28.985
-UH, YEAH, WELL SO
MUCH FOR SECRETS.

37:29.116 --> 37:31.901
HEY LOOK, THIS BOTTLE IS
MADE OUT OF CANDY AS WELL.

37:32.467 --> 37:34.687
THE TEMPERATURE HAS TO BE
EXACTLY RIGHT WHEN YOU MAKE IT.

37:34.817 --> 37:36.123
HOT, COOL, IT'S VERY CRITICAL.

37:36.254 --> 37:37.429
I MADE THIS ONE HERE.

37:37.559 --> 37:38.865
NOW WHAT I WANT YOU TO DO

37:38.995 --> 37:40.562
IS JUST HIT ME ON
THE HEAD WITH IT.

37:40.693 --> 37:42.434
-NO, I DON'T WANT TO.

37:42.564 --> 37:44.174
-IT'S JUST CANDY GLASS,
SO IT WON'T HURT ANYTHING.

37:44.305 --> 37:45.654
JUST CRACK THE
THING OVER MY HEAD.

