37:47.613 --> 37:48.831
-HIT ME ON THE HEAD!

37:59.668 --> 38:01.975
I'M ALL RIGHT, I'M ALL RIGHT.

38:02.715 --> 38:04.934
JUST COOKED THAT ONE
A LITTLE TOO LONG.

38:08.329 --> 38:10.723
AH, I'M GONNA SHOW
YOU THE PROPER WAY NOW

38:10.853 --> 38:13.029
TO DIVE THROUGH A
PLATE GLASS WINDOW.

38:13.160 --> 38:14.335
-I DON'T WANT TO WATCH THIS.

38:16.163 --> 38:18.948
-CLASSIC, HOLLYWOOD
MOVIE STUNT.

38:19.079 --> 38:20.559
GET READY, HERE I COME.

38:28.131 --> 38:30.830
-ED? ED?

38:37.532 --> 38:38.620
YOU OKAY?

38:38.751 --> 38:40.796
-UH, YEAH. I'M ALL RIGHT.

38:43.059 --> 38:47.107
-I'M OKAY. YEAH,
I'M ALL RIGHT.

